4/1/2017: Group of 6 canyoneers of all abilities. 3 hours. Thigh-deep water in potholes that could not be stemmed over. Wetsuits not needed. 1 rappel. The first drop was downclimbed by everyone. The second drop was downclimbed by half the group and handlined by the rest.
